title._content: Interior View of the All Aluminum Beer and Soft Drink Can Experimental House near Taos, New Mexico.

description._content: Original Caption: Interior View of the All Aluminum Beer and Soft Drink Can Experimental House near Taos, New Mexico. the Owners Report the House Seems to Work Well So Far and Gives the Feeling of Being Very Solid. the South Facing Windows Capture Heat from the Sun ...
